#
# Lab Network Topology
#
# ---------              ----------              ---------  
# |Client |__Client_NET__|Gateway |__Server_NET__|Server |
# ---------              ----------              --------- 
#                            |
#                            |Internet           
#                            |              ________ 
#                        ----------        /        \
#                        |External|________|Internet|
#                        |Router  |        \________/ 
